title: Elton John live in Australia. Pt. 2
brief_description: This concert, in December 1986, before a capacity audience in the Sydney Entertainment Centre, was part of the “Tour de Force” series. Elton and his band are accompanied by the Melbourne Symphony Orchestra under the baton of conductor James Newton Howard. Rated: G
